title: 807. Answering Draft Mysteries & Stocks to Buy in the Draft
itunes:title: 807. Answering Draft Mysteries & Stocks to Buy in the Draft
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys answer draft mysteries by going through 7 questions surrounding the draft. Next, the duo discuss the Ravens having 7 combined draft picks in the third and fourth round. To wrap up the show, the pair give draft prospect stocks they're buying.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
